title: Supremacy
description: After many tragedies, Lexi slowly heals from all her loss in "Warrior". A mischievous band of characters come to Pine Lake, bringing new magic from another place. After much heartache, loss and betrayal, Lexi finally finds her true soulmate. Just when things finally seem to go her way, chaos and turmoil once more overtake Pine Lake. New enemies take control, and Lexi is ripped away from the love of her life. After one final tragedy, Lexi goes face to face with death, which leads to a surprising end.
author: Kelsey Schaeffer
